{"tid":858054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍地盤疑籠𨋢急墜　水喉匠跌撞傷重亡","createTime":"2018-10-11T13:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T15:49:21.000Z","uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d70e240abb161c63febc8c0039c76a913d8508de","tid":858054,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"天水圍發生奪命工業意外。今日(11日)下午5時許，濕地公園路一私人住宅地盤，一名姓黃(62歲)男工人，乘搭俗稱「籠𨋢」的建築工地升降機運送物料時，籠𨋢疑突然急墜約一層，黃懷疑在𨋢內撞傷倒臥，陷入昏迷，工友見狀立即通知主管及報警求助。救護員接報趕至，將傷者送往天水圍醫院搶救，惜最終證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n事後死者多名工友及親友趕赴醫院了解，其中一名女親友驚聞噩耗後，突然癱軟跌倒，需由警員及親友攙扶，坐上輪椅。據現場消息指，死者為持牌水喉匠，同時為水喉舖東主，警方及相關部門正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處表示，在接報後即時派員到現場，現正就意外因展開調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181011/bkn-20181011183925713-1011_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181011%2Fbkn-20181011183925713-1011_00822_001.html&d=ZT14WKSIhssVYx4NoupFYf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6dd9c649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181011/bkn-20181011183925713-1011_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3770b479794b7c36f524e39f6d7a96ba4f40b628","tid":858054,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"多謝某人"},{"pid":"70246c8d64cfaa3e0c6586c922e7eaf51e679048","tid":858054,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"2c4694aa0dc10b3261aa3e3424ca4914931ee32d","tid":858054,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0015f22ec4aba96099197216a37285eb7d916f01","tid":858054,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"籠𨋢載人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd421f312ef7893703ae297050fceab6dc6f9ae3","tid":858054,"uid":10208,"like":0,